[Anastasia] It seems that I still can't use sorcery after all.
[Anastasia] As an immediate issue,

[Anastasia] First of all, there shouldn't be any problem as long as
there is no situation where I have to fight someone and sorcery is not
usable.

[Anastasia] If we can prevent the situation of falling into combat in
the first place, then there shouldn't be any problem.

[Anastasia] Even for sudden incidents, as long as I have magic items,
there shouldn't be any problem...

[Anastasia] Let's make thorough preparations in advance when fighting
against monsters.
[Anastasia] As the next issue,
[Anastasia] Regarding the enlarged sexual desire...
[Anastasia] I intend to have restraint when it comes to sexuality...

[Anastasia] If I can somehow manage to handle it myself at worst...
there shouldn't be any problem.
[Anastasia] ...........
[Anastasia] As long as these two points don't become a problem,

[Anastasia] The immediate task assigned to me is to find a way to undo
the curse that has been rewritten with magic.

[Anastasia] Also, if sorcery doesn't return to normal for a long period
of time, it will be almost impossible for me alone to rescue the
abducted students.
[Anastasia] I don't really want to think about it, but...

[Anastasia] Let's send a letter to my father asking for support from
other court sorcerers.

[Anastasia] There might be something that could serve as a clue at that
woman's mansion...

[Anastasia] First, let's investigate how to undo the curse at the Magic
Academy.
[Anastasia] There are also a few things that concern me...
